  <source>Nitromed</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A placebo-controlled trial of BiDil added to standard therapy in African-American patients
      with heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The overall objective is confirmation of BiDilâ€™s Safety and Efficacy in African-American
      (AFA) Patients with Moderate to Severe Symptomatic Heart Failure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
